thread.title_full: Blue Jays bury Hondo | New York Post

author: Hondo
title: Blue Jays bury Hondo
text:
Hondo took a thumping on Thursday, getting battered with the Blue Jays and smacked with Southern Cal to send the deficit skyrocketing to 1,642 agbayanis.
Friday night: In the battle of former former Red Sox beer and chicken buddies, Mr. Aitch will go with Lester, aka Jonny Lager, to chug past Lackey and the Cards — 20 units. Also, 20 on deGrom and the Mets to steal Game 1 against Kershaw, aka The Playoff Pushover. As for the NLDS wagers, he will stick with the Small Bears and Metamucils — 20 units apiece.
